Date 5 Jun 2001
From: ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>
Source: The Guardian, 31 May 2001 [edited

Total cases reported so far in the UK: 1665.
There have been 4 cases reported in Northern Ireland, which are included in
the above total. There have also been 2 cases reported in France, 25 in the
Netherlands, and one in Ireland.
